import React from 'react'
import './UserCard.css'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card'

const UserCard = ({ username, imageUrl, position, kills, deaths, asssists }) => {
    return (
        < Card className="card-user margin" >
            <Card.Img class="img" variant="left" src={imageUrl} />
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Title className="card-text">{username}</Card.Title>
                <Card.Text className="ca">{username}</Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card >
    )
}

export default UserCard
